{
  "poem": "When you're not near,\nMy heart feels so queer.\nI long to hold you tight,\nAnd bask in your sweet sight.\n\nYour smile, it brightens my day,\nYour laugh, it takes my breath away.\nI miss your gentle touch,\nOh, how I long for you so much.",
  "style": "Soft and romantic",
